{"word":"καταψήχω","slug":"καταψήχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταψήχω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to rub down, pound in a mortar</i>: — <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to crumble away</i>, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>κατέψηκται</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to stroke down, caress</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>mulceo</el>, <el>ἵππους</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}